@streamlineperformance6028 The point is, that they are not risking their lives. As they do not do in Formula 1 or Skydiving or cirque de soleil.
Formula 1 has seen significantly more fatalities than the U.S. Air Force Thunderbirds. But who would describe Nico Rossberg as a hero? People are dying, living their lives, smoking cigarettes, driving home.
Risking your life for propaganda, would be out of proportion.
